  <biospec_descr>
    <textblock>
      First we analyze the blood and articular fluid adipocytokines. If we can define a subset of
      patients characterized by a pattern of adipocytokines, genetic analysis will be performed
      later.
    </textblock>
  </biospec_descr>
  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        patients over 50 years who were referred for rheumatology for symptomatic knee
        osteoarthritis.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients over 50 years old with symptomatic knee osteoarthritis.

        Exclusion Criteria:

